I=E2=80=99ve been writing a series of posts to try to articulate the ways t=
hat I think social media, and Twitter in particular, has harmed political d=
iscourse in America. But the first post in the series remains the most well=
-read =E2=80=94 and, I think, the most original. It was called =E2=80=9CThe=
 Shouting Class [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVkM1uhSAQhZ_msruGf3HBo=
pu-hhlhVFovGMA2vn2xLpom87M4mTk5n4OKS8qn3VOp5BpjPXe0Eb_LhrViJkfBPAZvuaGCC0m8=
